headline: Useful Gifts - Not Luxury - Top Millennial and Gen Z Wish Lists This Holiday Season
summary: The countdown to the holidays is officially on, and this season more than three-quarters of Millennials want practical gifts for their homes, according to a new survey conducted by Morning Consult for The Home Depot. Beginning on October 28, customers can save on tools, smart home devices, appliances, home decor and more throughout the season – both in stores and online.

headline: 2 Mega-Cap Stocks Worth Your Attention and 1 We Question
summary: Megacap stocks dominate their sectors and their actions influence economies worldwide. The flip side though is that their sheer size means they have less room for explosive growth as scale works against them.
